Package net.fathomsoft.fathom.tree

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArgumentListNode
    TreeNode extension that keeps track of all of the arguments that are passed during a method call.
    ArrayAccessNode
    TreeNode extension that keeps track of any time an array is being accessed.
    ArrayNode
    IdentifierNode extension that contains the information describing an array instantiation.
    AssignmentNode
    TreeNode extension that contains information describing a variable assignment.
    BinaryOperatorNode
    TreeNode extension that represents the use of a binary operator.
    ClassNode
    DeclarationNode extension that represents the declaration of a class node type.
    ConditionNode
    TreeNode extension that represents a condition.
    ConstructorNode
    MethodNode extension that represents the declaration of a Constructor node type.
    DeclarationNode
    VariableNode extension that represents the declaration of a variable or method.
    DestructorNode
    MethodNode extension that represents the declaration of a Destructor node type.
    ElseStatementNode
    TreeNode extension that represents the declaration of an "else statement" node type.
    ExternalStatementNode
    TreeNode extension that represents an external statement.
    FileNode
    Class used to organize the Files that are fed to the compiler.
    ForLoopNode
    LoopNode extension that represents the declaration of a "for loop" node type.
    IdentifierNode
    TreeNode extension that represents an Identifier.
    IfStatementNode
    TreeNode extension that represents the declaration of an "if statement" node type.
    ImportListNode
    TreeNode extension that contains children of the type ImportNode.
    ImportNode
    TreeNode extension that represents the declaration of an "import statement" node type.
    InstantiationNode
    IdentifierNode extension that represents the declaration of an instantiation node type.

    TreeNode extension that represents a literal within the code.

    TreeNode extension that represents the initialization section of the for loop.

    TreeNode extension that represents the declaration of a LoopNode node type.
    LoopUpdateNode
    TreeNode extension that represents the update section of the for loop.
    MethodCallNode
    IdentifierNode extension that represents the declaration of a method call node type.
    MethodListNode
    TreeNode extension that represents all of the Methods within a class.
    MethodNode
    DeclarationNode extension that represents the declaration of a method node type.
    ModifierNode
    IdentifierNode extension that represents an identifier that can be a reference or pointer.
    OperatorNode
    TreeNode extension that represents an operator in an operation.
    ParameterListNode
    TreeNode extension that represents a list of parameters for a method.
    ParameterNode
    LocalVariableNode extension that represents a Parameter of a method.
    ProgramNode
    TreeNode extension that represents a whole Fathom program.
    ReturnNode
    TreeNode extension that represents a return statement node type.
    ScopeNode
    TreeNode extension that represents a scope of code.
    SyntaxTree
    Class that deconstructs a source code file and builds a Tree out of the statements.
    TreeNode
    Class that is the parent of all Nodes on the Tree.
    UnaryOperatorNode
    TreeNode extension that represents a unary operator node type.
    VTableNode

    WhileLoopNode
